          "treatment": "Permissive hypotension (SBP 80-90, no TBI). Massive transfusion protocol 1:1:1 (PRBC:FFP:Platelets). TXA 1g IV over 10 min then 1g over 8h. Limit crystalloid. Avoid hypothermia (warm fluids, blankets). Correct acidosis. Calcium replacement."
